<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>STORM: {{ topic }}</title>
  <style>
    :root { --accent:#e94560; --dark:#1a1a2e; --ink:#2a2a2a; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Pretendard','Apple SD Gothic Neo','Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;
           max-width: 880px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem; color: var(--ink);
           line-height: 1.75; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; }
    h1  { color: var(--dark); border-bottom: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-bottom: .5rem; line-height: 1.3; }
    h2  { color: #16213e; margin-top: 2.5rem; padding-left: .6rem; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent); }
    .meta { color: #666; font-size: .9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

    /* Step 1 — 페르소나 아코디언 (세로 글벽 → 한눈에 5개 조망) */
    .persona-accordion { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem; }
    .persona-item { border: 1px solid #e2e2e2; border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
                    border-radius: 6px; background: #fff; }
    .persona-item.timeout { border-left-color: #ccc; background: #f7f7f7; }
    .persona-item > summary { cursor: pointer; padding: .8rem 1rem; display: flex;
                    align-items: center; gap: .55rem; flex-wrap: wrap; list-style: none; }
    .persona-item > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .persona-item > summary::before { content: "\25B8"; color: var(--accent);
                    font-size: .85rem; transition: transform .15s; flex: 0 0 auto; }
    .persona-item[open] > summary::before { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .persona-item > summary:hover { background: #fafafa; border-radius: 6px; }
    .p-num { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
             width: 1.55rem; height: 1.55rem; background: var(--dark); color: #fff;
             border-radius: 50%; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; flex: 0 0 auto; }
    .p-role { font-weight: 700; color: #16213e; font-size: 1.02rem; }
    .badge { background: var(--dark); color: #fff; padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 12px;
             font-size: .72rem; }
    .p-judgment { flex: 1 1 100%; margin-left: 2.1rem; color: #555; font-size: .9rem; }
    .p-judgment.timeout-text { color: #aa3333; }
    .p-body { padding: .2rem 1.1rem 1.1rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: .2rem; }

    .contradiction { background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem; border-radius: 6px; }
    .synthesis   { background: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #43a047; padding: 1.4rem; border-radius: 8px; }
    .peer-review { background: #fce4ec; border-left: 4px solid #d81b60; padding: 1.4rem; border-radius: 8px; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 1rem 0; font-size: .92rem; }
    th, td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: .5rem .7rem; text-align: left; }
    th { background: #f4f4f4; }
    hr { margin: 2.5rem 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>&#128202; STORM Research Report</h1>
  <div class="meta">
    <strong>Topic:</strong> {{ topic }} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <strong>Generated:</strong> {{ generated_at }} &nbsp;|&nbsp;
    <strong>Method:</strong> Stanford STORM (Shao et al., NAACL 2024)
  </div>

  <h2>&#129309; Step 1: Multi-Perspective Analysis</h2>
  <p class="meta">각 페르소나 제목줄을 클릭하면 전문 분석이 펼쳐집니다. (요약줄 = 핵심 판정)</p>
  <div class="persona-accordion">
    {% for p in personas %}
    <details class="persona-item{% if p.timed_out %} timeout{% endif %}">
      <summary>
        <span class="p-num">{{ loop.index }}</span>
        <span class="p-role">{{ p.role }}</span>
        <span class="badge">{{ p.llm }}</span>
        {% if p.timed_out %}
          <span class="p-judgment timeout-text">&#9888;&#65039; 응답 없음 (타임아웃)</span>
        {% elif p.judgment %}
          <span class="p-judgment">{{ p.judgment }}</span>
        {% endif %}
      </summary>
      {% if not p.timed_out %}
      <div class="p-body">{{ p.content | safe }}</div>
      {% endif %}
    </details>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <h2>&#9889; Step 2: Contradictions &amp; Tensions</h2>
  <div class="contradiction">{{ contradictions | safe }}</div>

  <h2>&#128279; Step 3: Synthesis</h2>
  <div class="synthesis">{{ synthesis | safe }}</div>

  <h2>&#128269; Step 4: Peer Review</h2>
  <div class="peer-review">{{ peer_review | safe }}</div>

  <hr>
  <p style="color:#999;font-size:.8rem;">Generated by STORM Research Skill &mdash; KECC-ResearchLab</p>
</body>
</html>
